<PageTitle>SignSpeak</PageTitle>

<div class="landing-hero">
    <img src="image/SignSpeak-logo.jpeg" class="hero-logo" alt="SignSpeak logo" />
    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Breaking Barriers with Every Gesture</h1>
    <p class="lead">Real time American Sign Language translation powered by AI.</p>
    
    <div class="cta-buttons mt-4">
        <a href="Account/Register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 me-md-2">Get Started</a>
        <a href="Account/Login" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4">Log In</a>
    </div>
</div>

<hr class="my-5" />

<div class="landing-container">
    <section class="info-section">
        <h3>What is SignSpeak?</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">SignSpeak is a web-based application capable of translating American Sign Language (ASL) 
        gestures captured via video or image into text, and English text into ASL, using computer vision and machine learning for 
        translations to happen in real time.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="how-it-works mt-5">
        <h3>Quick Setup</h3>
        <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">1</div>
                <p>Sign up or Log in</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">2</div>
                <p>Open the Camera</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">3</div>
                <p>Start Signing</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>